cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.MM, cs.GR, cs.LG 

This paper deals with image processing techniques, specifically local histogram equalization. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves optimization techniques, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper discusses image quality metrics such as PSNR and SSIM, which could be relevant to cs.MM (Multimedia) or cs.GR (Graphics).
